header.gameNote: PAC-12 MEN'S TOURNAMENT PRES. BY NEW YORK LIFE - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: TJ Leaf sets the tone early in Las Vegas as he throws down a powerful dunk on USC.
videos.headline: Leaf punishes the rim

videos.description: Isaac Hamilton knocks down his third 3-pointer of the half against USC.
videos.headline: Hamilton feeling it early from deep

videos.description: Lonzo Ball plays some stingy defense as he swats a shot attempt into the bleachers.
videos.headline: Ball sends ball into the bleachers

videos.description: TJ Leaf out hustles USC on the boards, grabs his own rebound and scores.
videos.headline: Leaf grabs his own rebound, scores

videos.description: TJ Leaf shows USC his court vision with a pretty pass to Thomas Welsh for the dunk.
videos.headline: Leaf finds Welsh for the backdoor dunk

videos.description: Lonzo Ball kicks out a perfect pass to an open Bryce Alford who knocks down a record-setting 3-pointer for UCLA.
videos.headline: Ball drops a dime to Alford for 3-pointer

videos.description: Lonzo Ball knocks down a 3-pointer from ridiculously far back with a man in his face.
videos.headline: Ball buries a ridiculous 3-pointer from DEEP

videos.description: TJ Leaf continues to drop dimes as he feeds Thomas Welsh all alone for the slam.
videos.headline: Leaf finds wide open Welsh for the dunk

videos.description: Elijah Stewart elevates for the lob and throws down a ferocious dunk plus the foul.
videos.headline: Stewart throws down an insane and-1 alley-oop
